    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54B32 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This engine features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system, providing a visceral power band and an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M Differential Lock. Significant preventative maintenance has been completed, including a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a top-end refresh. The chassis retains its signature balance with a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension, offering precise turn-in and high-speed stability. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain remains tight and responsive, making this a quintessential driver's car for the performance-oriented enthusiast.",
